2.title: Artifactory calls by HTTP status
2.query:
fetch logs
| filter contains(content, "jfrog_artifactory")
| filter content.return_status != "null"
| makeTimeseries count = count(), by: { content.return_status }

3.title: Artifactory HTTP 4xx errors
3.query:
fetch logs
| filter contains(content, "jfrog_artifactory")
| filter startsWith(content.return_status, "4")
| makeTimeseries count = count(), by: { content.return_status }

4.title: Top requests by IP address
4.query:
fetch logs
| filter contains(content, "jfrog_artifactory")
| filter content.remote_address != "127.0.0.1"
| summarize count = count(), by: { content.remote_address }

6.title: Artifactory HTTP 5xx errors
6.query:
fetch logs
| filter contains(content, "jfrog_artifactory")
| filter startsWith(content.return_status, "5")
| makeTimeseries count = count(), by: { content.return_status }

9.title: User request activity
9.query:
fetch logs
| filter contains(content, "jfrog_artifactory")
| filter service.name == "jfrog.saas.rt.artifactory.request"
| filter NOT contains(content.user_name, "jfcon@") 
| filter NOT contains(content.user_name, "jfds@")
| filter NOT contains(content.user_name, "jfevt@")
| filter NOT contains(content.user_name, "jfisv@")
| filter NOT contains(content.user_name, "jfmc@")
| filter NOT contains(content.user_name, "jfob@")
| filter NOT contains(content.user_name, "jfxidx@")
| filter NOT contains(content.user_name, "jfxr@")
| filter NOT contains(content.user_name, "jfxr@")
| summarize count(), by: { 
  category = content.user_name, 
  content.return_status 
}

10.title: Log volume, number of records

12.title: Accessed resources by instance name
12.query:
fetch logs
| filter contains(content, "jfrog_artifactory")
| filter NOT contains(content.request_url, "/api/v1/system/")
| filter NOT contains(content.request_url, "/api/system/")
| filter NOT contains(content.request_url, "/api/v1/metrics")
| filter NOT contains(content.request_url, "/api/xray/")
| summarize count = count(), by: { content.request_url, host.id, content.user_name }

13.title: Accessed docker repos (top chart)
13.query:
fetch logs
| filter contains(content, "jfrog_artifactory")
| filter contains(content, "jfrog.saas.rt.artifactory.request")
| filter contains(content.request_url, "/manifests/")
| filter contains(content.request_method, "PUT") OR contains(content.request_method, "HEAD")
| summarize count = count(), by: { content.request_url }
| limit 30

14.title: Accessed docker repos (timeseries)
14.query:
fetch logs
| filter contains(content, "jfrog_artifactory")
| filter contains(content.request_url, "/manifests/")
| filter content.request_method == "PUT" OR content.request_method == "HEAD"
| makeTimeseries count = count(), by: { content.request_url }
